'''''Abouna''''' ( Arabic    , English: "Our Father") ni filimi yo muri  [[Cade|Chad]] yakinwe muri 2002,iyoborwa na  Mahamat Saleh Haroun . Yafatiwe amashusho ahitwa Gaoui na N'Djamena, Tchad.<ref>https://www.theguardian.com/culture/2002/nov/22/artsfeatures5</ref>

== Umugambi ==
Abahungu babiri (Tahir na Amine) babyutse mugitondo basanga se yataye umuryango wabo<ref>https://transmettrelecinema.com/film/abouna-notre-pere/</ref>. Barumiwe, batangira kwitwara nabi. Mugihe bareba  firime, batekereza ko babona se  avugana nabo ,bakiba firime kugirango babone izo kureba<ref>https://www.intofilm.org/films/3084</ref>. Nyina wabo (Achta) amaherezo yihebye maze abohereza ku ishuri rya Koran<ref>https://mountainx.com/movies/reviews/abouna-php/</ref>. Ntibishimye, bateganya guhunga kugeza umuhungu w'imfura akundana n'umukobwa utumva (Khalil)<ref>https://www.reseau-canope.fr/atelier-val-d-oise/cinema/Abouna</ref>.

== Gukina no gutanga umusaruro ==
Ahidjo Mahamat Moussa wakinnye Tahir wimyaka 15, yahawe abahungu ngo ahitemo gukina murumuna we Amine. Yahavuye ahitamo Hamza Moctar Aguid wimyaka umunani kuko yumvaga ko Aguid ashobora kuba murumuna we.<ref>https://www.screendaily.com/abouna-our-father/4011522.article</ref> Nyuma ya buri munsi wo gufata amashusho, film yoherejwe ibirometero 2600 i [[Paris]] kugirango itunganyirizwe<ref>https://www.kviff.com/en/programme/film/3/29-abouna</ref>. Gusa nyuma yo gutegereza iminsi myinshi, iyo ijambo ryagarukaga rivuga ko ntakibazo, gufata amashusho byarakomezaga. <ref>[https://www.bbc.co.uk/bbcfour/cinema/features/abouna.shtml ''Abouna''] by Josh Hillman, [[BBC Four]]</ref>

